Mişrātah

Mişrātah is a city in Misrata District, in Libya.

GPS Coordinates of Mişrātah, Misrata District, Libya

Mişrātah is located on the latitude of 32.37535 and longitude of 15.09254 and has a geohash of smf8pmy01dtm.

Cities and Towns near Mişrātah

The nearest significant population center from Mişrātah is Zliten in Misrata District, Libya, located 50 kilometers or 31 miles ← W of the city.

In total, we found 2 cities near Mişrātah in our database.
